Package main.java.questfortheabodeth.powerups

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AmmoPickup
    Ammo pickups give the player extra ammo for all the ammo pools that they currently hold.
    DamagePlus
    A pickup that increases the amount of damage the player does for a set amount of time.
    HealthBoost
    Health pickups increase the players current health up to a maximum of 100 points
    Pickup
    The base class for all pickups.
    ShieldPickup
    Adds a shield to the player.
    SpeedPickupUp
    Increases the players speed for a set amount of time and automatically changes it back after the time period has passed
    TheAbodeth
    The pickup that will end the game.
